<% header @matrix.name %>

<%= render 'layouts/progress', percent: 45 %>

<h5><b>Step 3:</b> What factors will determine your decision?</h5>
<div class="dec-form-description">
  <b>First,</b> determine which criteria or factors are important in your decision. Narrow this list down to a manageable size.
  For example:
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <ul>
        <li>The Big Dig: Go or No-Go?<br>
          <b>Criteria:</b>
          <span class="badge">Affordability</span>
          <span class="badge">Traffic Improvement</span>
          <span class="badge">Benefit to Society</span>
        </li>
        <li>What should we eat for dinner?<br>
          <b>Criteria:</b>
          <span class="badge">Flavor</span>
          <span class="badge">Time to Table</span>
          <span class="badge">Healthfulness</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <ul>
        <li>How should I prioritize my bucket list?<br>
          <b>Criteria:</b>
          <span class="badge">Low Risk</span>
          <span class="badge">Low Cost</span>
          <span class="badge">Awesomeness</span>
        </li>
        <li>Who should I nominate for the Supreme Court?<br>
          <b>Criteria:</b>
          <span class="badge">Experience</span>
          <span class="badge">Political Alignment</span>
          <span class="badge">Chance of Being Approved</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="dec-form-description">
  <b>Then,</b> for each criterium, select its relative importance. Each criterium will affect your decision outcome based on its importance.
</div>
<div class="dec-form-description">
  <b>Optionally,</b> you can customize the rating system for a criterium by clicking the 'customize criterium scores' link. By default, score of zero means 'poor' while a score of five means 'best'.
</div>
<%= render 'criteria/tip' %>

<%= render layout: 'form' do |f| %>
  <div id="criteria">
    <%= f.fields_for :criteria do |cf| %>
      <%= render 'criterium_fields', f: cf %>
    <% end %>
    <div class="links">
      <%= link_to_add_association 'Add Another Criterium', f, :criteria, class: 'btn btn-default' %>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
